 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-0",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# 2-3. 系统分析\n\n**System Analysis**\n\n---\n\n本notebook介绍通信系统的分析方法，包括系统函数、频率响应、稳定性判据等核心概念。系统分析是理解滤波器、调制器、信道等通信组件的基础工具。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-1",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. 学习目标\n\n- **理解系统函数**：传递函数H(z)的定义、零极点与系统特性的关系\n- **掌握频率响应**：幅度响应| H(e^jω)|和相位响应∠H(e^jω)的计算与分析\n- **稳定性判据**：利用极点位置判断系统稳定性\n- **群延迟分析**：线性相位与群延迟的关系\n- **系统级联**：多个系统级联时的总响应计算"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-2",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. 概念讲解\n\n### 2.1 系统函数与传递函数\n\n**系统函数H(z)**定义为系统输出Y(z)与输入X(z)的比值：\n\n$$H(z) = \\frac{Y(z)}{X(z)} = \\frac{b_0 + b_1 z^{-1} + \\cdots + b_M z^{-M}}{1 + a_1 z^{-1} + \\cdots + a_N z^{-N}}$$\n\n**零点**：分子多项式的根\n**极点**：分母多项式的根\n\n系统的频率响应：\n$$H(e^{j\\omega}) = H(z) \\big|_{z=e^{j\\omega}}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-3",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 2.2 稳定性判据\n\n**BIBO稳定性**：系统对任意有界输入都产生有界输出\n\n**判据**：离散系统稳定的充分必要条件是单位脉冲响应绝对可和：\n$$\\\sum_{n=-\\infty}^{\\infty} |h[n]| < \\infty$$\n\n**极点位置判据**：对于因果系统，所有极点必须在单位圆内（|极点| < 1）。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-4",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 2.3 群延迟\n\n**群延迟**定义为相位响应导数的负值：\n$$\\tau_g(\\omega) = -\\frac{d\\angle H(e^{j\\omega})}{d\\omega}$$\n\n群延迟衡量信号不同频率分量通过系统所需的时间，是衡量信号失真的重要指标。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-5",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. Python演示"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "id": "cell-6",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import numpy as np\nimport matplotlib.pyplot as plt\nfrom scipy import signal\n%matplotlib inline\n\nplt.rcParams['font.sans-serif'] = ['SimHei', 'DejaVu Sans']\nplt.rcParams['axes.unicode_minus'] = False\n\nprint(\"系统分析演示环境已准备就绪\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-7",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 3.1 系统函数与零极点分析"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "id": "cell-8",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 系统函数与零极点分析演示\ndef demo_zeros_poles():\n    \"\"\"\n    演示系统函数的零极点分析\n    \"\"\"\n    # 定义一个简单的IIR低通滤波器\n    # H(z) = 0.5 * (1 + z^{-1}) / (1 - 0.5*z^{-1})\n    b = np.array([0.5, 0.5])  # 分子系数\n    a = np.array([1, -0.5])  # 分母系数\n    \n    # 计算零极点\n    zeros = np.roots(b)\n    poles = np.roots(a)\n    \n    print(\"系统函数 H(z) = 0.5*(1 + z^{-1})/(1 - 0.5*z^{-1})\")\n    print(f\"\\n零点: {zeros}\")\n    print(f\"极点: {poles}\")\n    \n    # 可视化零极点图\n    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(8, 8))\n    \n    # 单位圆\n    theta = np.linspace(0, 2*np.pi, 100)\n    ax.plot(np.cos(theta), np.sin(theta), 'k--', linewidth=1, label='单位圆')\n    \n    # 零极点\n    ax.scatter(zeros.real, zeros.imag, marker='o', s=100, c='blue', \n               edgecolors='blue', linewidths=2, label=f'零点 (z={zeros[0]:.2f})', zorder=5)\n    ax.scatter(poles.real, poles.imag, marker='x', s=100, c='red', \n               linewidths=3, label=f'极点 (z={poles[0]:.2f})', zorder=5)\n    \n    ax.axhline(y=0, color='gray', linestyle='-', alpha=0.3)\n    ax.axvline(x=0, color='gray', linestyle='-', alpha=0.3)\n    ax.set_xlabel('实部', fontsize=11)\n    ax.set_ylabel('虚部', fontsize=11)\n    ax.set_title('零极点分布图', fontsize=12)\n    ax.legend(loc='upper right')\n    ax.grid(True, alpha=0.3)\n    ax.set_aspect('equal')\n    ax.set_xlim(-2, 2)\n    ax.set_ylim(-2, 2)\n    \n    plt.tight_layout()\n    plt.show()\n    \n    # 稳定性判断\n    is_stable = np.all(np.abs(poles) < 1)\n    print(f\"\\n系统稳定性: {'稳定 (所有极点在单位圆内)' if is_stable else '不稳定'}\")\n    \n    return b, a, zeros, poles, is_stable\n\nb, a, zeros, poles, is_stable = demo_zeros_poles()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-9",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 3.2 频率响应分析"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "id": "cell-10",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 频率响应分析演示\ndef demo_frequency_response():\n    \"\"\"\n    演示系统的幅度响应和相位响应\n    \"\"\"\n    # 定义一个低通滤波器\n    b = np.array([0.5, 0.5])\n    a = np.array([1, -0.5])\n    \n    # 计算频率响应\n    w, H = signal.freqz(b, a, worN=1024)\n    \n    # 幅度响应（dB）\n    H_mag = np.abs(H)\n    H_mag_db = 20 * np.log10(H_mag + 1e-10)\n    \n    # 相位响应\n    H_phase = np.angle(H)\n    \n    # 群延迟\n    H_phase_unwrapped = np.unwrap(H_phase)\n    group_delay = -np.diff(H_phase_unwrapped) / np.diff(w)\n    group_delay = np.append(group_delay, group_delay[-1])\n    \n    # 可视化\n    fig, axes = plt.subplots(3, 1, figsize=(10, 10))\n    \n    # 幅度响应\n    ax1 = axes[0]\n    ax1.plot(w/np.pi, H_mag_db, 'b-', linewidth=2)\n    ax1.set_xlabel('归一化频率 (×π rad/sample)', fontsize=11)\n    ax1.set_ylabel('幅度 (dB)', fontsize=11)\n    ax1.set_title('幅度响应 |H(e^{jω})|', fontsize=12)\n    ax1.grid(True, alpha=0.3)\n    ax1.set_xlim(0, 1)\n    ax1.axhline(y=-3.92, color='r', linestyle='--', alpha=0.7, label='-3.92dB截止点')\n    ax1.legend()\n    \n    # 相位响应\n    ax2 = axes[1]\n    ax2.plot(w/np.pi, H_phase, 'g-', linewidth=2)\n    ax2.set_xlabel('归一化频率 (×π rad/sample)', fontsize=11)\n    ax2.set_ylabel('相位 (rad)', fontsize=11)\n    ax2.set_title('相位响应 ∠H(e^{jω})', fontsize=12)\n    ax2.grid(True, alpha=0.3)\n    ax2.set_xlim(0, 1)\n    \n    # 群延迟\n    ax3 = axes[2]\n    ax3.plot(w/np.pi, group_delay, 'r-', linewidth=2)\n    ax3.set_xlabel('归一化频率 (×π rad/sample)', fontsize=11)\n    ax3.set_ylabel('群延迟 (samples)', fontsize=11)\n    ax3.set_title('群延迟', fontsize=12)\n    ax3.grid(True, alpha=0.3)\n    ax3.set_xlim(0, 1)\n    \n    plt.tight_layout()\n    plt.show()\n    \n    # 计算-3dB截止频率\n    idx_3db = np.argmin(np.abs(H_mag_db - (-3)))\n    wc_3db = w[idx_3db] / np.pi\n    print(f\"-3dB截止频率: {wc_3db:.3f} × π rad/sample\")\n    print(f\"对应模拟频率: {wc_3db * 0.5:.3f} × Fs\")\n    \n    return w, H_mag_db, H_phase, group_delay\n\nw, H_mag_db, H_phase, group_delay = demo_frequency_response()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-11",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 3.3 系统级联分析"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "id": "cell-12",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 系统级联演示\ndef demo_system_cascade():\n    \"\"\"\n    演示两个系统级联时的总响应\n    \"\"\"\n    # 系统1: FIR低通\n    b1 = np.array([0.5, 0.5])\n    a1 = np.array([1])\n    \n    # 系统2: IIR低通\n    b2 = np.array([0.2, 0.2])\n    a2 = np.array([1, -0.8])\n    \n    # 级联后的系统系数（卷积）\n    b_cascade = np.convolve(b1, b2)\n    a_cascade = np.convolve(a1, a2)\n    \n    print(\"系统1: H1(z) = 0.5*(1 + z^{-1})\")\n    print(\"系统2: H2(z) = 0.2*(1 + z^{-1})/(1 - 0.8*z^{-1})\")\n    print(f\"\\n级联系统: H(z) = H1(z) * H2(z)\")\n    print(f\"分子系数: {b_cascade}\")\n    print(f\"分母系数: {a_cascade}\")\n    \n    # 计算频率响应\n    w1, H1 = signal.freqz(b1, a1)\n    w2, H2 = signal.freqz(b2, a2)\n    _, H_cascade = signal.freqz(b_cascade, a_cascade)\n    \n    # 可视化\n    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 5))\n    \n    ax.plot(w1/np.pi, 20*np.log10(np.abs(H1)+1e-10), 'b--', linewidth=2, \n            label='系统1', alpha=0.7)\n    ax.plot(w2/np.pi, 20*np.log10(np.abs(H2)+1e-10), 'g--', linewidth=2, \n            label='系统2', alpha=0.7)\n    ax.plot(w1/np.pi, 20*np.log10(np.abs(H_cascade)+1e-10), 'r-', linewidth=2, \n            label='级联系统')\n    \n    ax.set_xlabel('归一化频率 (×π rad/sample)', fontsize=11)\n    ax.set_ylabel('幅度 (dB)', fontsize=11)\n    ax.set_title('系统级联的频率响应', fontsize=12)\n    ax.legend()\n    ax.grid(True, alpha=0.3)\n    ax.set_xlim(0, 1)\n    \n    plt.tight_layout()\n    plt.show()\n    \n    return b_cascade, a_cascade\n\nb_cascade, a_cascade = demo_system_cascade()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-13",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 4. 思考题\n\n1. **零极点与频率响应**：如果一个系统的零点在单位圆上，频率响应会有什么特点？\n2. **稳定性分析**：判断以下系统的稳定性：\n   - H(z) = 1/(1 - 1.5*z^{-1})\n   - H(z) = 1/(1 - 0.9*z^{-1})\n3. **群延迟**：线性相位系统的群延迟有什么特点？为什么这在通信中很重要？\n4. **系统级联**：两个稳定系统级联后是否一定稳定？证明你的结论。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-14",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n\n## 总结\n\n本notebook介绍了系统分析的基本方法：\n- **系统函数**通过零极点描述系统特性\n- **极点位置**决定系统稳定性（稳定 iff 所有极点在单位圆内）\n- **频率响应**分析包括幅度响应、相位响应和群延迟\n- **系统级联**的总响应等于各系统响应的乘积"
   ]
  }
 ],
